Entries.default: "Well, that's a first. Can't feel my hands anymore, but at least I can say I did it."
"Quite a climb, ac, but we have found quite a vantage."
"Nothing like a little exercise to warm the extremities."
"Well well, the view was worth the climb."
"Maybe they'll be friendly. You never know until you meet them."
"Gods a-fucking-live! You know this be twice as tall to me as it be to the rest of you swabbies, aye?"
"A frozen coast. How... familiar. Let us finish this quickly, ja?"
"My legs're about ready to fall off, but gods damn if this view isn't worth it."
"We should drag Worthless Idiot up here and shove him off the edge."
"This is taller even than the mountains of Lipasalis!"
